text: Krista Fanedl (born 1 August 1941) is a Slovenian alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1964 Winter Olympics, representing Yugoslavia. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Slovenian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Yugoslavia Category:Alpine skiers at the 1964 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Maribor
